{"tid":906202,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"hall有死智障仔真係好撚辛苦 （小長文）","createTime":"2018-11-17T18:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T22:57:41.000Z","uid":218468,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f690ecc5b20b880771fd181fb3084ca36cf20e","tid":906202,"uid":218468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:27:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUk大學dorm 廚房共用 5間房 一人一間房<br />\n開學頭幾星期加埋我得4個人 好融洽好正常<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母 冇幾耐有個死智障仔搬咗入嚟<br />\n形容下外表 肥柒毒黑暗瘡 個頭長期縮 成個龜頭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勁撚冇禮貌 第一次見面招呼都唔打聲<br />\n就叫我幫佢搬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔該都冇句 彩佢都on9<br />\n<br />\n第一日 公用kettle就咁隊個嘴埋去飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚇到我尻都縮埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 咁我地都嘗試了解下佢<br />\n傾左陣 佢突然講「我覺得你地好老，我唔想同你地熟，會有gap。」我地呆撚左望住大家 問兩問先知佢先細我地一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你20歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我先21<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> wtf?<br />\n<br />\n最撚慶係 前排俾我哋發現佢亂咁用我哋啲嘢 開我地啲櫃桶攞調味料用 勁撚順手開個櫃桶 拎啲刀刀叉叉出嚟用 問都冇問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直到佢洗緊既時候先發現 問佢 問問下又發現佢攞人地啲洗潔精黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一人一枝自己買自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日又亂咁搞我哋雪櫃啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢自己啲嘢擺晒落我哋度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n次次屌親佢就成個智障dup哂頭點頭話好好好 好你老母 好你就做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同學校投訴過 佢地don't give a fuck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1e831984cb13b658360d17fd25b2dab70d5869","tid":906202,"uid":195975,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"唔好蝦毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094ba797d48673d74143e4cffec8825fc9259e00","tid":906202,"uid":198998,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:35:34.000Z","msg":"落好多鹽/瀉藥落去個kettle兜水度 <br />\n擺糖個樽擺鹽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09deed0e88ce4af7aa4efb7e3499118297a8222","tid":906202,"uid":87043,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:35:35.000Z","msg":"夾手夾腳玩鳩佢啦<br />\n橫掂都dont give a fuck"},{"pid":"76ff9e62f1cc7ad45eeacca0c884ca6aa7c81f0d","tid":906202,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:36:22.000Z","msg":"係..係..係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083b9fda6535a4e073fba79ef204b8fb20a59103","tid":906202,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:36:38.000Z","msg":"好..好..好..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f8cc4fd906b23f911fd81b3f95850ed8753d43","tid":906202,"uid":35598,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:37:15.000Z","msg":"盜竊罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a050ec76ec889617f6dcfb9454705d17e83cd2d","tid":906202,"uid":216127,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:39:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cfd920f5406e08b976c587256b8c86f49747795","tid":906202,"uid":195975,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:41:37.000Z","msg":"親佢去沖涼 鎖房門唔比佢入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d8e706f20c4358067a676163612b6e36129